articles.title: Doctors reveal troubling signs in early flu trends, warn of ‘unusually bad’ season - AOL.com
articles.description: Health experts warn this flu season could be unusually severe, with early spread and concerning H3N2 strain activity across the U.S. following Australia's worst flu season.
articles.content:
This years flu season is already raising alarms among public health officials and infectious disease experts.
